msgid ""
"The links for an application are stored as <link href=\"https://www."
"freedesktop.org/software/appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-"
"url\"><code>&lt;url&gt;</code></link> elements within the application’s "
"<code>&lt;component&gt;</code> in its metainfo file."
msgstr ""
"Et programs links gemmes som <link href=\"https://www.freedesktop.org/"
"software/appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-url\"><code>&lt;url&gt;</"
"code>-elementer inden for programmets <code>&lt;component&gt;</code> i dets "
"metainfofil."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:322
msgid ""
"Add as many of the link types documented in the <link href=\"https://www."
"freedesktop.org/software/appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-"
"url\">appstream specification</link> as are available for the application. "
"If no suitable page exists for a given link type, it doesn’t have to be "
"included."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj så mange af de linktyper, der er beskrevet i <link href=\"https://www."
"freedesktop.org/software/appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-"
"url\">appstream-specifikationen</link>, som findes til programmet. Hvis der "
"ikke findes en passende side til en given linktype, behøver den ikke at "
"blive medtaget."

